                              @{u}@{b}ICON TOOLTYPES:@{ub}@{uu}

 @{u}Tooltype       Function                                GUI Gadget         @{uu}

 MODE           Mode of cdxSizer (SUPER/XWIN/SIMPLE)    "Mode"
 QUALIFIERł     Extra key(s) to activate move-mode      "Move qualifier"
